      *
       ERROR-MESSAGE SECTION.
       ERROR-000.
             MOVE 2815 TO POS.
             DISPLAY "                                      " AT POS.
             DISPLAY WS-MESSAGE AT 2815 WITH reverse-video BLINK
                BELL FOREGROUND-COLOR IS 4.
             CALL "C$SLEEP" USING 1.
       ERROR-010.
      *       CALL "&LOCKKBD" USING F-FIELDNAME.
       ERROR-020.
             MOVE " " TO WS-MESSAGE.
             DISPLAY WS-MESSAGE AT 2815.
       ERROR-999.
             EXIT.
      *
